{"type": "article", "id": 18241, "title": "可移动的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-30T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115202fhKEcjqudae26Py5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是丹麦设计师 Marie Hesseldahl 为丹麦品牌 Muuto 带来的一盏可移动的灯。它的灯座相当于一个夹子，可以从任何角度夹在书架上。而灯罩的外形较为特别，像是将圆筒灯罩从中心向对称两边削尖，从不同的角度看有不同的形状，类似一顶帽子，有未来感。灯罩和灯座是统一的颜色，小巧而多功能的特征都体现了北欧风格。<a href=\"http://www.mariehesseldahl.com/#/snap-light/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115200yMI7E3xY8zGbCuaj.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"861\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115200NXapFqIs6bjgE0W3.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"850\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115201sgqzHY3NbTJ5wcmP.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"425\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021152017pht19EdgQLTF8xj.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"510\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115202IcRZj3eWd5fx9O7H.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"899\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}